  "title": "(Fast Start!) Junior Events Marketing- office hours🌍",
  "description": "<p>🚀 What You Need to do:</p>\n<ul>\n  <li>Deliver captivating in-person presentations on both B2C and B2B platforms<br>\nDevelop, implement, and oversee sales and marketing plans to assist the group in reaching goals.🎯</li>\n  <li>Identify what the customers want and offer the best goods and services.</li>\n  <li>Provide clear, understandable information and a transparent and open sales process.</li>\n</ul>\n<p><br></p>\n<p>👀You have what we are looking for:</p>\n<ul>\n  <li>An active student mentality, always eager to learn and grow with the company 📚<br>\nStrong determination and mindset overcoming hurdles to succeed.</li>\n  <li>Adaptable and able to keep up in a fast-paced environment⚡️</li>\n</ul>\n<p><br></p>\n<p>🎁 Your benefits &amp; opportunities:</p>\n<ul>\n  <li>Guided and laid out growth plans based on your performance</li>\n  <li>Working in a family &amp; friends-like environment<br>\nMentorship provided—0 experience will be trained by the experience leader</li>\n  <li>Get your passport ready to travel with us internationally ✈️</li>\n</ul>\n<p><br></p>\n<p>💡 Get ready to start right now!</p>\n<p>Nothing is more expensive than a missed opportunity! click APPLY NOW!</p>",
