    "description": "<p>We are a small family of dreamers, driven by the same vision: to bring on positive changes to the sales &amp; marketing industry.<br>\n<br>\nOur strength lies in our diversity of backgrounds, interests and cultures as a team. We work in an open office environment, which fosters interactions and fast-paced decisions.<br>\n<br>\nWe favour ability and a can-do mindset over experience and degrees.<br>\n<br>\nSo, if you are ...<br>\n<br>\n- tired of corporate jobs and want to go maverick<br>\n- a go-getter and usually says “I’ll do it !”<br>\n- in a habit of learning new things<br>\n<br>\nDrop everything and apply now because we’re expanding our family! \"</p>",
